    "description": "Are you a skilled Full Stack Developer looking for your next big career move? iGate India Global Group in Indore offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout iGate India Global Group:\niGate India Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Integrate third-party APIs and services\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in Python\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Indore, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with iGate India Global Group!",
